sql_text: SELECT  FROM [TPC-DS Benchmark Model] WHERE ([Measures].[m_ss_quantity_sum]) CELL PROPERTIES VALUE, FORMAT_STRING, LANGUAGE, BACK_COLOR, FORE_COLOR, FONT_FLAGS

SELECT NON EMPTY
Hierarchize(DrilldownMember({{DrilldownLevel({[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].[All]},,,INCLUDE_CALC_MEMBERS)}},
{[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Calendar Year].&[1998],
[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Calendar Year].&[2001],
[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Calendar Year].&[2003]},,,INCLUDE_CALC_MEMBERS))
DIMENSION PROPERTIES PARENT_UNIQUE_NAME,
HIERARCHY_UNIQUE_NAME ON COLUMNS
FROM [TPC-DS Benchmark Model] CELL PROPERTIES VALUE, FORMAT_STRING, LANGUAGE, BACK_COLOR, FORE_COLOR, FONT_FLAGS

SELECT {[Measures].[m_cs_ext_sales_price_sum],
[Measures].[m_cs_ext_tax_sum],
[Measures].[m_cs_ext_discount_amt_sum]}
DIMENSION PROPERTIES PARENT_UNIQUE_NAME,HIERARCHY_UNIQUE_NAME ON COLUMNS ,
NON EMPTY
CrossJoin(CrossJoin(Hierarchize({DrilldownLevel({[Catalog_Sales_Price_Tier].[Catalog Sales Price Tier].[All]},,,INCLUDE_CALC_MEMBERS)}),
Hierarchize({DrilldownLevel({[Customer Address].[Customer Address].[All]},,,INCLUDE_CALC_MEMBERS)})),
Hierarchize({DrilldownLevel({[Customer Demographics].[Customer Demographics].[All]},,,INCLUDE_CALC_MEMBERS)}))
DIMENSION PROPERTIES PARENT_UNIQUE_NAME,HIERARCHY_UNIQUE_NAME ON ROWS
FROM [TPC-DS Benchmark Model] CELL PROPERTIES VALUE, FORMAT_STRING, LANGUAGE, BACK_COLOR, FORE_COLOR, FONT_FLAGS
EVALUATE ROW("Avg Unit Net Profit", [Average Catalog Unit Net Profit])
